file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: SwaggerPetstore
  version: 1.0.6
servers:
  - url: /
security:
  - default: []
paths:
  /pet/findByStatus:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          headers:
            x-wso2-example:
              style: simple
              explode: false
              example: example header value
          content:
            application/json:
              example:
                - id: 0
                  name: doggie
                  status: available
                - id: 1
                  name: kitty
                  status: available
      security:
        - default: []
      x-auth-type: Application & Application User
      x-throttling-tier: Unlimited
      x-wso2-application-security:
        security-types:
          - oauth2
        optional: false
  /pet/{petId}:
    get:
      parameters:
        - name: petId
          in: path
          required: true
          style: simple
          explode: false
          schema:
            type: string
            format: string
      responses:
        "50X":
          description: Service Unavailable
          headers:
            x-wso2-example:
              style: simple
              explode: false
              example: example header value
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                ref1:
                  value:
                    some response: Ref 1 Service Unavailable
                ref2:
                  value:
                    another response: Ref 2 Service Unavailable
        default:
          description: default response
          headers:
            x-wso2-example:
              style: simple
              explode: false
              example: default header value
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                ref1:
                  value:
                    id: 0
                    name: doggie
                    status: available
                ref2:
                  value:
                    id: 1
                    name: kitty
                    status: available
      security:
        - default: []
      x-auth-type: Application & Application User
      x-throttling-tier: Unlimited
      x-wso2-application-security:
        security-types:
          - oauth2
        optional: false
components:
  securitySchemes:
    default:
      type: oauth2
      flows:
        implicit:
          authorizationUrl: https://test.com
          scopes: {}
x-wso2-auth-header: Authorization
x-wso2-basePath: /v3/1.0.6
